quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  40,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  40,1,Haa-Meeem
  40,2,is kitaab ka utaara jana khuday-e ghalib o daana ki taraf se hai
  40,3,jo gunah bakhsnay wala aur tauba qubool karne wala hai aur sakht azaab dainay wala aur sahib karam hai. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi. isi ki taraf phir kar jana hai
  40,4,khuda ki aayton mein wohi log jhagarte hain jo kafir hain. to un logon ka shehron mein chalna phirna tumhe dhokay mein nah daal day
  40,5,un se pehlay Nooh ki qoum aur un ke baad aur amtoN ne bhi ( payghambaroon ki ) takzieeb ki. aur har aُmt ne apne paighambar ke baray mein yahi qasadkiya ke is ko pakar len aur behooda ( sh_hbat se ) jhagarte rahay ke is se haq ko zael kar dein to mein ne un ko pakar liya ( so dekh lau ) mera azaab kaisa howa
  40,6,aur isi terhan kafiroon ke baray mein bhi tumahray perwar-digaar ki baat poori hochuki hai ke woh ahal dozakh hain
  40,7,jo log arsh ko uthaye hue aur jo is ke gurda gird ( halqa bandhay hue ) hain ( yani farishtay ) woh apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh karte rehtay hain aur mominoun ke liye bakhshish mangte rehtay hain. ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar teri rehmat aur tera ilm har cheez ko ihata kiye hue hai to jin logon ne tauba ki aur tairay raste par chalay un ko bakhash day aur dozakh ke azaab se bchale
  40,8,ae hamaray perwar-digaar un ko hamesha rehne ke bahishtoon mein daakhil kar jin ka tunay un se wadakiya hai aur jo un ke baap dada aur un ki biwion aur un ki aulaad mein se naik hon un ko bhi. be shak to ghalib hikmat wala hai
  40,9,aur un ko azabon se bachaaye rakh. aur jis ko to is roz azabon se bacha le ga to be shak is par meharbani farmai aur yahi barri kamyabi hai
  40,10,jin logon ne kufarkiya un se pukaar kar keh diya jaye ga ke jab tum ( duniya mein ) imaan ki taraf bulaye jatay they aur mantay nahi they to khuda is se kahin ziyada bezaar hota tha jis qader tum apne aap se bezaar ho rahay ho
  40,11,woh kahin ge ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar to ne hum ko do dafaa be jaankiya aur do dafaa jaan bakhsh. hum ko apne gunaaho ka iqraar hai tokiya niklny ki koi Sabeel hai ?
  40,12,yeh is liye ke jab tanha khuda ko puraka jata tha to tum inkaar kardete they. aur agar is ke sath shareek muqarrarkiya jata tha to tasleem kar lete they to hukum to khuda hi ka hai jo ( sab se ) oopar aur ( sab se ) bara hai
  40,13,wohi to hai jo tum ko apni nishanain dekhata hai aur tum par aasman se rizaq utaarta hai. aur nasiyaat to wohi pokarta hai jo ( is ki taraf ) rujoo karta hai
  40,14,to khuda ki ibadat ko khalis kar kar usi ko poukaro agarchay kafir bura hi manen
  40,15,maalik darjaat aali aur sahib arsh hai. apne bundon mein se jis par chahta hai apne hukum se wahi bhejta hai taakay mulaqaat ke din se draway
  40,16,jis roz woh nikal parrin ge un ki koi cheez khuda se makhfi nah rahay gi. aaj kis ki badshahat hai? khuda ki jo akela aur ghalib hai
  40,17,aaj ke din har shakhs ko is ke aamaal ka badla diya jaye ga. aaj ( kisi ke haq mein ) be insafi nahi hogi. be shak khuda jald hisaab lainay wala hai
  40,18,aur un ko qareeb anay walay din se dra-o jab ke dil gham se bhar kar gulon taq arhay hon ge. ( aur ) zaalmon ka koi dost nah hoga aur nah koi safarishi jis ki baat qubool ki jaye
  40,19,woh aankhon ki khayanat ko jaanta hai aur jo ( baatein ) seenon mein posheeda hain ( un ko bhi )
  40,20,aur khuda sachaai ke sath hukum farmata hai aur jin ko yeh log pkarte hain woh kuch bhi hukum nahi day satke. be shak khuda suneney wala ( aur ) dekhnay wala hai
  40,21,kiya unhon ne zameen mein sair nahi ki taakay dekh letay ke jo log un se pehlay they un ka injaam kaisa howa. woh un se zor aur zameen mein nishanaat ( bananay ) ke lehaaz se kahin barh kar they to khuda ne un ko un ke gunaaho ke sabab pakar liya. aur un ko khuda ( ke azaab ) se koi bhi bachanay wala nah tha
  40,22,yeh is liye ke un ke paas paighambar khuli daleelen laatay they to yeh kufar karte they so khuda ne un ko pakar liya. be shak woh sahib qowat ( aur ) sakht azaab dainay wala hai
  40,23,aur hum ne moose ko apni nishanain aur Daleel roshan day kar bheja
  40,24,( yani ) firaon aur Haman aur qaroon ki taraf to unhon ne kaha ke yeh to jadugar hai jhoota
  40,25,gharz jab woh un ke paas hamari taraf se haq le kar puhanche to kehnay lagey ke jo is ke sath ( khuda par ) imaan laaye hain un ke beiton ko qatal kardo aur baityon ko zindah rehne do. aur kafiroon ki tadbeerye be thikaane hoti hain
  40,26,aur firaon bola ke mujhe chhorro ke moose ko qatal kardoon aur woh apne perwar-digaar ko blale. mujhe dar hai ke woh ( kahin ) tumahray deen ko nah badal day ya malik mein fasaad ( nah ) peda kardey
  40,27,moose ne kaha ke mein har mutaqabbir se jo hisaab ke din ( yani qayamat ) par imaan nahi lata. apne aur tumahray perwar-digaar ki panah le chuka hon
  40,28,aur firaon ke logon mein se aik momin shakhs jo apne imaan ko posheeda rakhta tha kehnay lagakiya tum aisay shakhs ko qatal karna chahtay ho jo kehta hai ke mera perwar-digaar khuda hai aur woh tumahray perwar-digaar ( ki taraf ) se nishanain bhi le kar aaya hai. aur agar woh jhoota hoga to is ke jhoot ka zarrar isi ko hoga. aur agar sacha hoga to koi sa azaab jis ka woh tum se wada karta hai tum par waqay ho kar rahay ga. be shak khuda is shakhs ko hadaayat nahi deta jo be lehaaz jhoota hai
  40,29,ae qoum aaj tumhari hi badshahat hai aur tum hi malik mein ghalib ho. ( lekin ) agar hum par khuda ka azaab agaya to ( is ke daur karne ke liye ) hamari madad kon kere ga. firaon ne kaha ke mein tumhe wohi baat smjhata hon jo mujhe sojhi hai aur wohi raah batata hon jis mein bhalai hai
  40,30,to jo momin tha woh kehnay laga ke ae qoum mujhe tumhari nisbat khauf hai ke ( mbada ) tum par aur ummton ki terhan ke din ka azaab aajay
  40,31,yani ) Nooh ki qoum aur Aad aur smod aur jo log un ke peechay hue hain un ke haal ki terhan ( tumhara haal nah hojaye ) aur khuda to bundon par zulm karna nahi chahta
  40,32,aur ae qoum mujhe tumhari nisbat pukaar ke din ( yani qayamat ) ka khauf hai
  40,33,jis din tum peeth phair kar ( qayamat ke din se ) bhago ge ( is din ) tum ko koi ( azaab ) khuda se bachanay wala nah hoga. aur jis shakhs ko khuda gumraah kere is ko koi hadaayat dainay wala nahi
  40,34,aur pehlay Yousuf bhi tumahray paas nishanain le kar aeye they to jo woh laaye they is se tum hamesha shak hi mein rahay. yahan taq ke jab woh faut hogaye to tum kehnay lagey ke khuda is ke baad kabhi koi paighambar nahi beje ga. isi terhan khuda is shakhs ko gumraah kar deta hai jo hadd se nikal jaane wala aur shak karne wala ho
  40,35,jo log baghair is ke ke un ke paas koi Daleel aayi ho khuda ki aayton mein jhagarte hain. khuda ke nazdeek aur mominoun ke nazdeek yeh jhagra sakht napasand hai. isi terhan khuda har mutaqabbir sarkash ke dil par mohar laga deta hai
  40,36,aur firaon ne kaha ke Haman mere liye aik mehal banaao taakay mein ( is par charh kar ) rustoon par poanch jaoon
  40,37,"( yani ) asmano ke rustoon par, phir moose ke khuda ko dekh lon aur mein to usay jhoota samjhta hon. aur isi terhan firaon ko is ke aamaal bad achay maloom hotay they aur woh raste se rok diya gaya tha. aur firaon ki tadbeer to be car thi"
  40,38,aur woh shakhs jo momin tha is ne kaha ke bhayio mere peechay chalo mein tumhe bhalai ka rasta dikhao n
  40,39,bhayio yeh duniya ki zindagi ( chand roza ) faida uthany ki cheez hai. aur jo akhirat hai wohi hamesha rehne ka ghar hai
  40,40,jo buray kaam kere ga is ko badla bhi waisa hi miley ga. aur jo naik kaam kere ga mard ho ya aurat aur woh sahib imaan bhi hoga to aisay log bahisht mein daakhil hon ge wahan un ko be shumaar rizaq miley ga
  40,41,aur ae qoum merakiya ( haal ) hai ke mein tum ko nijaat ki taraf bulaataa hon aur tum mujhe ( dozakh ki ) aag ki taraf bulatay ho
  40,42,tum mujhe is liye bulatay ho ke khuda ke sath kufar karoon aur is cheez ko is ka shareek muqarrar karoon jis ka mujhe kuch bhi ilm nahi. aur mein tum ko ( khuday-e ) ghalib ( aur ) bakhsnay walay ki taraf bulaataa hon
  40,43,sach to yeh hai ke jis cheez ki taraf tum mujhe bulatay ho is ko duniya aur akhirat mein bulanay ( yani dua qubool karne ) ka Maqdoor nahi aur hum ko khuda ki taraf lootna hai aur hadd se nikal jaane walay dozakhi hain
  40,44,jo baat mein tum se kehta hon tum usay agay chal kar yaad karo ge. aur mein apna kaam khuda ke supurd karta hon. be shak khuda bundon ko dekhnay wala hai
  40,45,gharz khuda ne moose ko un logon ki tdbiron ki buraiyon se mehfooz rakha aur firaon walon ko buray azaab ne aa ghera
  40,46,yani ) aatish ( jahannum ) ke subah vsham is ke samnay paish kiye jatay hain. aur jis roz qayamat barpaa hogi ( hukum hoga ke ) firaon walon ko nihayat sakht azaab mein daakhil karo
  40,47,aur jab woh dozakh mein jhagrain ge to adna darjay ke log barray admion se kahin ge ke hum to tumahray tabay they tokiya tum dozakh ( ke azaab ) ka kuch hissa hum se daur kar saktay ho ?
  40,48,barray aadmi kahin ge ke tum ( bhi aur ) hum ( bhi ) sab dozakh mein ( rahen ge ) khuda bundon mein faisla karchuka hai
  40,49,aur jo log aag mein ( jal rahay ) hon ge woh dozakh ke daroghon se kahin ge ke apne perwar-digaar se dua karo ke aik roz to hum se azaab halka kardey
  40,50,woh kahin ge kekiya tumahray paas tumahray paighambar nishanain le kar nahi aeye they. woh kahin ge kyun nahi to woh kahin ge ke tum hi dua karo. aur kafiroon ki dua ( is roz ) be car hogi
  40,51,hum apne payghambaroon ki aur jo log imaan laaye hain un ki duniya ki zindagi mein bhi madad karte hain aur jis din gawah kharray hon ge ( yani qayamat ko bhi )
  40,52,jis din zaalmon ko un ki moazrat kuch faida nah day gi aur un ke liye laanat aur bura ghar hai
  40,53,aur hum ne moose ko hadaayat ( ki kitaab ) di aur bani Israel ko is kitaab ka waris banaya
  40,54,aqal walon ke liye hadaayat aur nasiyaat hai
  40,55,to sabr karo be shak khuda ka wada sacha hai aur apne gunaaho ki maffi mango aur subah vsham apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh karte raho
  40,56,jo log baghair kisi Daleel ke jo un ke paas aayi ho khuda ki aayton mein jhagarte hain un ke dilon mein aur kuch nahi (iradah ) Azmat hai aur woh is ko pounchanay walay nahi to khuda ki panah mango. be shak woh suneney wala ( aur ) dekhnay wala hai
  40,57,asmano aur zameen ka peda karna logon ke peda karne ki nisbat bara ( kaam ) hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  40,58,aur andha aur aankhh wala barabar nahi. aur nah imaan laane walay nekokaar aur nah badkaar ( barabar hain ) ( haqeeqat yeh hai ke ) tum bohat kam ghhor karte ho
  40,59,qayamat anay wali hai is mein kuch shak nahi. lekin aksar log imaan nahi rakhtay
  40,60,aur tumahray perwar-digaar ne kaha hai ke tum mujh se dua karo mein tumhari ( dua ) qubool karoon ga. jo log meri ibadat se Azrah taqqabur kanyatay hain. anqareeb jahannum mein zaleel ho kar daakhil hon ge
  40,61,khuda hi to hai jis ne tumahray liye raat banai ke is mein aaraam karo aur din ko roshan banaya ( ke is mein kaam karo ) be shak khuda logon par fazl karne wala hai. lekin aksar log shukar nahi karte
  40,62,yahi khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai jo har cheez ka peda karne wala hai. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi phir tum kahan bhatak rahay ho ?
  40,63,isi terhan woh log bhatak rahay they jo khuda ki aayton se inkaar karte they
  40,64,khuda hi to hai jis ne zameen ko tumahray liye tehrnay ki jagah aur aasman ko chhat banaya aur tumhari soorten banayen aur soorten bhi khoob banayen aur tumhe pakeeza cheeze khanay ko den. yahi khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai. pas khuday-e perwar-digaar aalam bohat hi babarkat hai
  40,65,woh zindah hai ( jisay mout nahi ) is ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi to is ki ibadat ko khalis kar kar isi ko poukaro. har terhan ki tareef khuda hi ko ( sazawar ) hai jo tamam Jahan ka perwar-digaar hai
  40,66,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam un se ) keh do ke mujhe is baat ki momanat ki gayi hai ke jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho un ki parastish karoon ( aur mein un ki kyonkr parastish karoon ) jab ke mere paas mere perwar-digaar ( ki taraf ) se khuli daleelen aa chuki hain aur mujh ko yeh hukum howa hai ke perwar-digaar aalam hi ka tabay farmaan hon
  40,67,wohi to hai jis ne tum ko ( pehlay ) matti se peda kiya. phir nutfa bana kar phir lothrha bana kar phir tum ko nkalta hai ( ke tum ) bachay ( hotay ho ) phir tum apni jawani ko pahunchte ho. phir boorhay ho jatay ho. aur koi tum mein se pehlay hi mrjata hai aur tum ( mout ke ) waqt muqarrar taq poanch jatay ho aur taakay tum samjhoo
  40,68,wohi to hai jo jalataa hai aur maarta hai. phir jab woh koi kaam karna ( aur kisi ko peda karna ) chahta hai to is se keh deta hai ke hoja to woh jata hai
  40,69,kiya tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jo khuda ki aayton mein jhagarte hain. yeh kahan bhatak rahay hain ?
  40,70,jin logon ne kitaab ( khuda ) ko aur jo kuch hum ne payghambaroon ko day kar bheja is ko jhtlaya. woh anqareeb maloom karlen ge
  40,71,jab ke un ki gardnon mein taoq aur zanjeeren hon gi ( aur ) ghsite jayen ge
  40,72,( yani ) kholtey hue pani mein. phir aag mein jhonk diye jayen ge
  40,73,phir un se kaha jaye ga ke woh kahan hain jin ko tum ( khuda ke ) shareek banatay they
  40,74,( yani ghair khuda ) kahin ge woh to hum se jatay rahay balkay hum to pehlay kisi cheez ko pkarte hi nahi they. isi terhan khuda kafiroon ko gumraah karta hai
  40,75,yeh is ka badla hai ke tum zameen mein haq ke baghair ( yani is ke khilaaf ) khush howa karte they aur is ki ( saza hai ) ke itrayea karte they
  40,76,( ab ) jahannum ke darwazon mein daakhil hojao. hamesha isi mein raho ge. mtkbron kakiya bura thikana hai
  40,77,to ( ae paighambar ) sabr karo khuda ka wada sacha hai. agar hum tum ko kuch is mein se dikha den jis ka hum tum se wada karte hain. ( yani kafiroon par azaab nazil karen ) ya tumhari muddat hayaat poori kar dein to un ko hamari hi taraf lout kar aana hai
  40,78,aur hum ne tum se pehlay ( bohat se ) paighambar beje. un mein kuch to aisay hain jin ke halaat tum se bayan kar diye hain aur kuch aisay hain jin ke halaat bayan nahi kiye. aur kisi paighambar ka Maqdoor nah tha ke khuda ke hukum ke siwa koi nishani laaye. phir jab khuda ka hukum aap_hncha to insaaf ke sath faisla kardiya gaya aur ahal baatil nuqsaan mein par gay
  40,79,khuda hi to hai jis ne tumahray liye charpaye banaye taakay un mein se baaz par sawaar ho aur baaz ko tum khatay ho
  40,80,aur tumahray liye un mein ( aur bhi ) faiday hain aur is liye bhi ke ( kahin jaane ki ) tumahray dilon mein jo haajat ho un par ( charh kar wahan ) poanch jao. aur un par aur kashtiyon par tum sawaar hotay ho
  40,81,aur woh tumhe apni nishanain dekhata hai to tum khuda ki kin kin nshanyon ko nah manu ge
  40,82,kiya un logon ne zameen mein sair nahi ki taakay dekhte jo log un se pehlay they un ka injaam kaisa howa. ( halaank ) woh un se kahin ziyada taaqatwar aur zameen mein nishanaat ( bananay ) ke aitbaar se bohat barh kar they. to jo kuch woh karte they woh un ke kuch kaam nah aaya
  40,83,aur jab un ke paighambar un ke paas khuli nishanain le kar aeye to jo ilm ( apne khayaal mein ) un ke paas tha is par itranay lagey aur jis cheez se tamaskhurkiya karte they is ne un ko aa ghaira
  40,84,phir jab unhon ne hamara azaab dekh liya to kehnay lagey ke hum khuday-e wahid par imaan laaye aur jis cheez ko is ke sath shareek banatay they is se na muta'qid hue
  40,85,lekin jab woh hamara azaab dekh chuke ( is waqt ) un ke imaan ne un ko kuch bhi faida nah diya. ( yeh ) khuda ki aadat ( hai ) jo is ke bundon ( ke baray ) mein chali aati hai. aur wahan kafir ghatay mein par gay
